Summary: Biochemical reaction from dolutegravir to dolutegravir M1. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from dolutegravir to dolutegravir glucuronide. This interaction can be catalyzed by UGT1A1, UGT1A3 or UGT1A9.
Transport from dolutegravir to dolutegravir. This interaction can be catalyzed by ABCB1 or ABCG2.
